text:
It's location is next to Vathapatirai Kaaliamman Temple. Very near to Bus Stop.
Ideal for conducting Bhajans. But as it is towards Serangoon Road, there is lot of noise from Vehicles.
The place was rented by us for 2hrs during we weekends to teach Sanskrit to kids.
Nice little space to worship for Sri Guru Ragavendra Swamy.
Very nice temple guru blessings  is there for all guruway saranam
